A Roblox character model. They wear a beret with three metal piercings and a chain attachment. Their hair is a black, messy mullet. Around their head are two black intersecting halos with red eyes along their outer rims. These halos are obscuring most of the character's face, except for their smile, They wear a black long-sleeved crop top with a white partially-zipped up puffer jacket that hangs off their shoulders. The jacket has two white belts hanging off the hem. They also wear a black skirt with black thigh-high boots.
